# ðŸ• Case Study #2 Pizza Runner

## ðŸ Solution - B. Runner and Customer Experience

### What are the standard ingredients for each pizza?

````sql
select pt.topping_name
from pizza_names pn
join
pizza_recipes pr
on pn.pizza_id = pr.pizza_id
join pizza_toppings pt
on pr.topping = pt.topping_id
where pr.topping in (
	select topping
    from pizza_recipes
    group by topping
    having count(pizza_id) > 1)
group by pt.topping_name;

````

**Answer:**



### 2. What was the average time in minutes it took for each runner to arrive at the Pizza Runner HQ to pickup the order?

````sql
select r.runner_id, avg(timestampdiff(minute, c.order_time, r.pickup_time)) as avg_time_taken
from customer_orders_temp c
left join runner_orders_temp r
on c.order_id = r.order_id
where r.distance is not null
group by r.runner_id;
````

**Answer:**

